playing a critical role in shaping several successful startups' product strategies and designs in the mortgage, business intelligence, and education sectors. \",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"His expertise in these areas is evident in the accolades and achievements of the companies he has worked with.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Callis is highly skilled with an education from the prestigious MIT and Sloan School of Management. He has also completed several cohorts at the Stanford D school, further honing his skills in design and innovation.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"But Callis's contributions to the industry go far beyond his professional accomplishments.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"},{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"He is passionate about teaching and mentoring, teaching coding and UX design to over 5,000 students. He is also actively engaged in cultivating new talent by sharing his knowledge and network.\\\"\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"email\":\"ben@impactgrowthlabs.com\",\"role\":\"Founder\",\"photo\":{\"metadata\":{\"tags\":[],\"concepts\":[]},\"sys\":{\"space\":{\"sys\":{\"type\":\"Link\",\"linkType\":\"Space\",\"id\":\"lp5y22r82q1h\"}},\"id\":\"4LXcqB6AJoWsdoJ1OSHFov\",\"type\":\"Asset\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-01T20:25:58.758Z\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-01T20:25:58.758Z\",\"environment\":{\"sys\":{\"id\":\"master\",\"type\":\"Link\",\"linkType\":\"Environment\"}},\"publishedVersion\":8,\"revision\":1,\"locale\":\"en-US\"},\"fields\":{\"title\":\"Benjamin Callis Avatar\",\"description\":\"Profile picture of Benajmin Callis\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lp5y22r82q1h/4LXcqB6AJo